Example :-
Input:
N = 6
arr[] = 7 10 4 3 20 15
K = 3
Output : 7
Explanation :
3rd smallest element in the given 
array is 7.

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

int ans=-1;
        Arrays.sort(arr); //first all arr i sorted ascending order than ckeck last Kth element and i fount it than i return. 
        for(int i=0;i<k;i++) 
        {
            ans=arr[i];
        }
        return ans;
